    "In this light, the concept of false detections entering the catalogue becomes less of a concern, although in some studies, analysts may prefer to work with only high-confidence events.",
    "When possible, we label each event with a verified source.",
    "We use the Pratt et al. (2014) catalogue of stick-slip events for cross-comparison with the reference event catalogue.",
    "Taking uncertainties in start time into account, we label 140 events as stick-slip.",
    "Four of those events are determined as additional to the Pratt et al. (2014) catalogue from a manual reconnaissance."
  ],
